ProxMox Setup for PCIe Passthrough (Supermicro H12SSL-I, AMD Epyc Cpu)

Ensure IOMMO + SR-IOV are enabled in BIOS

-Load VFIO modules at boot-

nano /etc/modules-load.d/vfio.conf 

vfio
vfio_iommu_type1
vfio_pci
vfio_virqfd

Save file and close


-Apply all changes-

update-initramfs -u -k all

--REBOOT--
